<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<catalogue library="false" id="14ba-fba9-02a2-388d" name="Craftworld Eldar" gameSystemId="sys-c49b-9f87-36f1-c9b5" gameSystemRevision="6" revision="53" battleScribeVersion="2.03" type="catalogue" xmlns="http://www.battlescribe.net/schema/catalogueSchema">
  <sharedRules>
    <rule name="Roaming Performers" id="c56f-e048-3acd-ec3d" hidden="false">
      <description>You may add one of the following Harlequins units to your Army


List:
● TROUPE MASTER
● SHADOWSEER
and one of either:
● LIGHT TROUPE
● DARK TROUPE
● TWILIGHT TROUPE


If you do add one or more of those units to your Army List, your Army Rules gains Mocking Misstep, Allegro Advance, Prismatic Pirouette and Kaleidoscopic Cavalcade.</description>
    </rule>
    <rule name=" Aspect (X)" id="9db0-7796-725a-f91f" hidden="false">
      <description>While this unit is ready, after each of your End steps, if this was not your second turn in a row, you may take another turn. If you do, you must select a unit with Aspect Warrior to activate that turn.</description>
    </rule>
    <rule name="Eyes of the Asuryani" id="3be3-6578-1b0d-7468" hidden="false">
      <description>While this unit is not active, enemy units visible to this unit gain the following ability:

Fatal Thread: For each attack made by an Aeldari Craftworlds unit that targets this unit, a Hit Roll of 6 for that attack always wounds.</description>
    </rule>
  </sharedRules>
