          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit finishes an Advance within 4” of the centre point of a vault, you may roll 1 D6. Then select one of your units and it gains the relic which matches the result. Any other friendly unit with that relic loses it.</characteristic>
