            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit’s Attack step, if one or more enemy units that were targeted by an attack made by this unit this turn had Fatal Thread, this unit may Reposition.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Jetbike Mastery" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="d6e4-305c-cf4f-3a1d">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit finishes an Advance, if each of its models is 10” or more from where it started this turn, this unit gains the following ability until the next time it Activates:

Speeding Blur: For each attack that targets this unit, the Hit Roll for that attack is worsened by 1.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
