      <profiles>
        <profile name="Aggressive Defence" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="0850-b0eb-beeb-769e">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit&apos;s Attacks step, if an enemy unit was destroyed this turn, this unit may Advance.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Flickerjump" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="6232-4d13-e751-1939">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">If this unit would Advance, you may instead use ‘flickerjump’. If you do, you may remove this unit from the battlefield and place it into reserves. Then, Deploy it anywhere in the battlefield outside of the engagement range of enemy units. If you do, roll a D6 for each model in this unit and for each 1, this unit suffers 2 SW.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Hunter’s Snare" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="22ad-0d0a-fa67-ff48">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After you Activate this unit, select an enemy unit not visible to this unit. Until the End step, for each attack that targets the selected unit, add 1 to the Hit Roll.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
    </selectionEntry>
