            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit finishes an Advance within engagement range of any enemy units with Fatal Thread, until the End step, this unit gains each selected ability:

Shining Thrust: For each attack made by this unit, add 1 to the Hit Roll for that attack.

