          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After your active unit Disembarks from within this unit, until the End step, for each attack made by that unit, reroll Wound Rolls of 1 for that attack.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Cloudstrike" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="bd78-0368-18dc-316f">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit is Activated in reserves, you may use ‘cloudstrike’. If you do, roll 3D6. Then, Deploy this unit anywhere on the battlefield at least X” away from all enemy units where X is the result of that roll. If you do, during this turn’s Move step, do not make a Move roll and this unit cannot Advance or Reposition.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
