          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Must Attach to" typeId="2c63-5e3f-9132-459d">This unit must attach to either:
a) GUARDIAN DEFENDERS
b) Any unit with an Aspect, X ability</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Master of Paths" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="66e8-f0b8-afbc-7715">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">This unit may attach to any unit with Aspect Warrior.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Path of Command" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="7afc-930e-bada-9178">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After any of your units with Aspect Warrior Activate, you may select an enemy unit visible to one or more friendly units with Eyes of the Asuryani. If you do, until the End step, that friendly unit gains Fluid Grace, and that enemy unit gains Graceless Foes.


Fluid Grace: During this unit’s Move step, for each Move Roll made for this unit, add 2D6 to that roll.


Graceless Foes: For each attack made targeting this unit, reroll Hit Roll of 1 for that attack.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
